Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.11,0:00:04.68,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,The {\i1}Shirase{\i0} leaves port \Nin Japan in mid-November,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.21,0:00:08.10,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,heads south across the \Nocean towards Antarctica,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:11.61,sign_143_5_Fremantle,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2860,1)}Fremantle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:11.61,sign_143_6_Arrival_Departur,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2860,1)}Arrival\NDeparture
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:11.61,sign_144_7_Fremantle,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2860,1)}Fremantle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:11.61,sign_144_8_Sidney,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2860,1)}Sidney
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:11.61,sign_143_9_Sidney,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2860,1)}Sidney
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:11.61,sign_197_9_Cross_the_55th_P,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2860,1)}Cross the 55th Parallel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.10,0:00:10.20,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,and makes a port call \Nin Fremantle on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.20,0:00:11.61,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Australia!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.84,0:00:15.64,Main,shia,0000,0000,0000,,There, they'll resupply and bring \Nthe expedition members on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.64,0:00:19.80,Main,shia,0000,0000,0000,,Then as December begins, they'll set \Ncourse for the continent of Antarctica.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.80,0:00:22.04,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,The people don't board in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.04,0:00:23.50,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,They haven't done that for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:29.75,sign_564_21_Fremantle_______,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Fremantle           Sidney
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.86,0:00:26.14,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Nowadays, people typically \Nboard at Fremantle,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.14,0:00:29.13,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,then fly home from Sidney.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.29,0:00:33.83,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,So while the {\i1}Shirase{\i0} is in port there,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.83,0:00:37.51,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,we'll want to take a plane \Nfrom Japan to Fremantle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:40.82,sign_930_24_Fremantle,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1000)}Fremantle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:41.91,sign_930_25_Cross_the_55th_P,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1000)}Cross the 55th Parallel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.13,0:00:44.02,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll board the {\i1}Shirase{\i0}... \Nand head for Antarctica.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:44.02,sign_1055_27_Showa_Station,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,1)}Syowa Station
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:44.02,sign_1020_28_Depart_Showa_Sta,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}Depart Syowa Station
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.69,0:00:47.15,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Will they let us on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.15,0:00:50.74,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Antarctic expeditions are \Ntypically a state enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.74,0:00:52.96,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,The boat is manned by the SDF,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.96,0:00:57.03,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,and the expedition members have to \Npass strict screenings and training.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.70,0:00:59.75,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,High schoolers would never be allowed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.74,0:01:01.54,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.54,0:01:04.29,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,This year is special.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.49,0:01:06.16,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,What's this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:12.30,sign_1602_37_Civilian_Antarct,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Civilian Antarctic Expedition to Take Place for the\NFirst Time in Three Years\N{\b0\fs14}A revival of the "Antarctic Challenge,"\N the first civilian Antarctic expedition held\Nthree years ago, has been announced.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.80,0:01:12.30,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,"Civilian Antarctic Expedition to Take \NPlace for the First Time in Three Years"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.96,0:01:20.68,Italics,kim,0000,0000,0000,,The moment I saw that smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.35,0:01:23.43,Italics,kim,0000,0000,0000,,I felt a shiver run through my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.97,0:01:27.86,Italics,kim,0000,0000,0000,,"Is this what trembling with \Nanticipation means?" I wondered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.68,0:01:32.44,Italics,kim,0000,0000,0000,,I'm currently making the \Nmost preposterous, absurd,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.44,0:01:34.82,Italics,kim,0000,0000,0000,,and enormous plans I've ever made.
