Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:23.93,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Looking for part-time work?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:25.85,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Morning. And yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:28.49,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I told you about the cost of \Nthe plane ticket yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.49,0:03:30.52,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase-chan wants me to earn it in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:32.21,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Antarctica, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:35.86,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. She also said, since I'll \Nhave to take time off from school,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:38.65,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I should attend every day now while I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:40.53,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look! This one's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:41.15,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:43.63,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,They're hiring high school-aged girls! \NIt's in the hospitality industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.63,0:03:47.38,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It's a job where you talk to boys \Nand go on walks with them and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:51.81,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,If you do really well, you could \Neven make a million yen per month...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:54.71,Main,megu,0000,0000,0000,,If they catch you, you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:56.44,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:03:59.21,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I'll turn in a part-time job \Npermission form to the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:01.22,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,You're so ignorant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:05.60,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Setting the money aside, do you \Nreally think they'll let you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:07.88,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Shirase-chan told me all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:13.10,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,She's got some friends on the civilian \NAntarctic expedition that's going this year, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:17.52,chalk,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Easy on Hands\NSincerity Chalk
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.38,0:04:21.53,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,I did some research, \Nand it sounds a little dicey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:26.78,sign_6271_78_Struggles_to_Fun,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,765)}Struggles to Fund Civilian Antarctic Expedition
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:24.71,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,"Four years ago, with the \Ncompletion of new stations
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.71,0:04:27.96,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,and commissioning of a new icebreaker ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.96,0:04:32.66,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,the {\i1}Shirase II{\i0} and Syowa Station \Nwere sold to civilian interests,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:36.42,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,but they've struggled with \Nmaintenance and operation costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:40.39,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,The expedition members and sponsor companies
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.39,0:04:42.79,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,involved in the last \Nexpedition three years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.79,0:04:45.68,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,have also been announcing \Ntheir withdrawal one by one,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:50.01,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,and the safety of participants \Nmay not be ensured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:53.77,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, more and more voices are \Nspeaking up against the project itself"...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.48,0:04:53.77,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tamaki-san! Tamaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.68,0:04:57.40,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:05:00.90,sign_7131_90_Analyzing_the_as,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Analyzing the assertions of...\N\NWhy does he assert that love and\Ncourage are everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.51,0:05:00.90,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Would you kindly read the next passage?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:01.67,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:04.84,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,"This, combined with the financial problems, \Nis causing concern regarding"— Wagh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:12.91,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,And what comes after "Wagh"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:13.91,sign_7503_96_Rose_Rose_Rose_R,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Rose Rose Rose Rose Rose Rose Rose Rose
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:14.66,sign_7503_96_Rose_Rose_Rose_R,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Lemon Lemon Lemon Lemon \NLemon Lemon Lemon Lemon
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:15.66,sign_7503_96_Rose_Rose_Rose_R,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Depression Depression Depression Depression \NDepression Depression Depression
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:18.70,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Still so much to write...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:21.46,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't had to write lines \Nsince elementary school...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:23.55,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't have been reading it in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:26.19,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,But I just couldn't wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.19,0:05:26.84,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,So, what else?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.14,0:05:28.93,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:32.93,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,For now, there's nothing about \Nthe project being canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:34.25,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Then, it's okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:35.75,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:42.36,sign_8032_108_We_lend_manga,sign,0000,0000,0000,,We lend manga
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:39.71,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it hasn't been canceled, it won't \Nbe that simple for you to get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:41.97,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,Just because it's for civilians \Ndoesn't change that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.97,0:05:45.20,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but Shirase-chan is the \Ndaughter of an expedition member!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.20,0:05:47.86,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like getting \Nfamily seats at a concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:51.39,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,They're not gonna let you \Non the ship that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.39,0:05:52.98,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.51,0:05:54.62,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,You're probably right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.23,0:05:58.12,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to see her soon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:06:01.11,Main,meg,0000,0000,0000,,You should just ask her straight up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.33,0:06:04.29,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:04.84,sign_8712_119_Depression_Depre,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Depression Depression \NDepression Depression Got it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:09.38,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.38,0:06:10.94,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Punctuality is crucial.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.94,0:06:12.81,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,That goes double when we're in Antarctica.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:15.23,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,A few minutes can mean the \Ndifference between life or death.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.23,0:06:18.94,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,But I told you, the teacher got mad at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:19.95,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.59,0:06:22.27,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to pick one by today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:24.42,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.42,0:06:27.66,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Look, it's just the cost of \Na ticket to Australia, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.66,0:06:29.80,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I can scrape up the \Nmoney over summer vacation...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:32.91,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,You should have as much money \Nas possible, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:34.74,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Here, I looked for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:36.04,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:37.25,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Girls in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:39.19,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,A job in the hospitality industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:42.77,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,You talk to boys and go on \Nwalks with them, it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:44.25,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Nice wage, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:46.76,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.06,0:06:49.01,Italics,girls,0000,0000,0000,,Here come the PonPon Girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:52.73,Italics,mem,0000,0000,0000,,If you hit the jackpot, \Nyou can take me home with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:56.52,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.83,0:07:00.09,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Megu-chan had to \Ntell me about it, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.09,0:07:03.26,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you can be pretty stupid \Nsometimes, too, Shirase-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.47,0:07:04.22,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm not stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.22,0:07:05.52,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I just didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:06.78,sign_10203_145_High_School_Girl,sign,0000,0000,0000,,High School Girl Outing Requests\N{\fs12}Michika's Diary\N{\c&H9257F4&}T-san, thanks for always asking for me!\N{\c&H1A1C37&}I went out with T-san and Tada who always ask for me!\NI said I love barbecue, so he took me out to that famous restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:06.78,sign_10205_146_New_Message_Did_,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(190,1)}New Message\NDid you ask Antarctica?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.14,0:07:10.28,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:12.28,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,A friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:15.60,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,She's worried about whether or \Nnot they'll really let us go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.05,0:07:17.28,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,You don't believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.28,0:07:19.04,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I don't believe you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:22.88,sign_10527_152_Well__no_big__An,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no big\N\NAntarctic News\N{\c&HB5CDA8&}\N\N{\c&H7596A0&}Did you ask Antarctica?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:22.56,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no guarantee, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:24.79,sign_10619_154_Struggles_to_Fun,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Struggles to Fund Civilian Antarctic Expedition
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:28.05,Main,sign,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:28.05,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's pretty worrying, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.62,0:07:32.91,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,And even if it isn't canceled, \Nwe don't know if they'll let us join...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:33.55,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,They will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:37.49,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the daughter of \NKobuchizawa Takako, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.49,0:07:38.60,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.11,0:07:40.65,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Is that enough to qualify?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.65,0:07:42.46,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I assure you, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:45.37,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,You think so? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.37,0:07:48.36,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to do this \Nanymore, you can just say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:51.49,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you try to blame it on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:55.73,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I don't want to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.73,0:07:57.24,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't want to fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:08:00.50,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to think \N"I just shouldn't have bothered!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:05.25,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I would rather think "I wish I'd gone!" \N"I wish I'd followed Shirase-chan's plan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:34.72,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I really am aware of the whole situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.72,0:08:36.45,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I've thought up a plan, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:37.59,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.59,0:08:38.55,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:42.72,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain the whole thing, so you \Nshould keep making your preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.72,0:08:44.45,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:51.09,sign_12693_176_Part_time_Employ,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(524,1)}Part-time Employees Wanted
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:52.51,sign_12739_177_I_got_a_job_,sign,0000,0000,0000,,I got a job!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:08:54.49,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.49,0:08:56.93,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wish me to warm that up for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:09:00.58,Main,emp,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you can learn it as you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:02.39,Main,emp,0000,0000,0000,,First, handle the restocking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:04.29,Main,emp,0000,0000,0000,,Miyake-san over there \Nwill tell you what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:05.19,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:08.58,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:13.07,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'm Tamaki. I'm joining \Nthe team as of today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:15.18,Main,sign,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to working with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:16.13,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Tamaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:17.34,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Tamaki Mari.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:19.07,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's why you're "Kimari".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.65,0:09:23.74,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Miyake Hinata.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.74,0:09:24.52,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,How old're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:26.29,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Sixteen. Second year high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:29.60,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Same here! Nice to meetcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:33.92,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,L-Likewise...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.65,0:09:36.30,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,You go to Tatara Nishi High, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:37.88,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, "Tanishi."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:39.58,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Why the sudden need for a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:43.26,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,There's a place I want \Nto go, so I need money.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.38,0:09:47.44,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Would that place happen to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:50.44,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Antarctica?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:55.94,sign_14157_201_Polar_Drink,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Polar\NDrink
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:55.94,sign_14157_202_Weddell_Seal_Sod,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Weddell Seal\NSoda
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.84,0:10:02.95,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,You want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:07.16,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, apparently she's been \Nlistening in on our conversations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:11.00,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you make it sound \Nlike I did it on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:14.34,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't eavesdropping. \NYou two were just talking so loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:15.84,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:18.22,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,"If you don't want to do this, just say so!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:19.97,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,"It's not that I don't want to do it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.17,0:10:21.97,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Enough! We get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:23.64,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,That piqued my curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.29,0:10:27.16,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Then straight after, \NKimari came in to get a job, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:30.74,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,And I got to thinking, it's gotta be destiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.74,0:10:32.67,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Just to be clear, this isn't a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:33.85,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.85,0:10:37.60,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous, and you \Nneed to pay your own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:40.75,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading out in December, so you'll \Nneed to take time off from school, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.75,0:10:43.05,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay! It's all good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.05,0:10:45.98,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,I've got money from my job, \Nand I don't go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.98,0:10:47.16,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,What, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:49.29,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that surprising, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:51.46,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,You see them from time to time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.06,0:10:54.55,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Sixteen-year-olds who don't go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:58.25,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get the wrong idea, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.25,0:11:00.42,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm as smart as anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:02.46,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,I got my high school certificate
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.46,0:11:04.93,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,and I got an A rating \Nin the recent mock exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:07.31,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,And you're still only in your second year?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:09.36,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean you're going to college?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.36,0:11:10.26,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.26,0:11:13.54,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,My current dream is to ace \Neverything and show up everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.54,0:11:17.03,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,who goofs off in high school and fails!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:21.70,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,But then how would you have \Ntime to go to Antarctica?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:22.91,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,A reasonable question,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:25.90,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,but I still have almost two \Nyears before entrance exams,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.90,0:11:29.26,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,and when I think about how I'll spend \Nnext year knuckling down for exams,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:31.33,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,it makes me want to do something \Nspecial while I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.33,0:11:32.77,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I get you! I so get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:34.92,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't do it this year, \Nyou'll never get another chance, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:36.42,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:40.44,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, must my sixteenth year come and go,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.44,0:11:42.52,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,with nothing but meat buns \Nand oden to show for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.52,0:11:43.43,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.54,0:11:46.97,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to have a drink out with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:48.11,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I don't drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.11,0:11:49.47,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.09,0:11:51.02,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:54.58,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one making the plans here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:56.07,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,You need to follow my instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.35,0:11:58.59,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,We never said we wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:12:00.49,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is she the irritable type?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:01.70,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,A tad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:06.07,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,This describes my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.82,0:12:09.83,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,We'll put it into action this Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.61,0:12:12.25,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,This Sunday, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:13.08,Main,both,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.68,0:12:15.23,Main,both,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:27.01,sign_17705_258_How_d_it_go_,sign,0000,0000,0000,,How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.40,0:12:21.43,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of her plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.43,0:12:22.36,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:25.44,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like it'll be pretty tricky...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.09,0:12:27.93,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it does...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:32.86,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,But she knows a lot more \Nabout Antarctica than we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.86,0:12:34.69,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,so it seems to me that we might as well try.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:37.52,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,"If you can still turn back, \Nit's not really a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.97,0:12:43.16,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,When you hit the point of no return, \Nthat's the moment it becomes a journey."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.88,0:12:45.40,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like a quote!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.40,0:12:46.45,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Who said it originally?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:47.49,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:48.54,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.23,0:12:51.45,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.94,0:12:57.45,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,I've always liked you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.45,0:13:01.56,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,You know? My store's close to Tanishi, \Nso students come in all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.56,0:13:02.21,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.49,0:13:05.82,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,But you two seemed different, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.53,0:13:08.60,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a different sort of vibe, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:12.22,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,No one's ever said that to me before...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:17.76,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,I really hate the thought \Nof blending in with a crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.76,0:13:20.48,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I couldn't handle high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:23.64,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,I really envied you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.29,0:13:26.00,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Envied what about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:28.62,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Hard to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:31.63,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,The honesty, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:35.75,sign_19500_286_Normal,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,1)}Normal
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:35.75,sign_19500_287_Kuki,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,1)}Kuki
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:40.29,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel sufficiently flattered?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:41.62,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:46.24,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,That's how Hinata-chan works \Nher way into your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:47.26,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.94,0:13:48.95,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:02.86,sign_20161_293_Well__we_ll_do_t,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we'll do the best we can
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:15.10,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Shinjuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.58,0:14:17.75,sign_20490_295_Shinjuku_Station,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Shinjuku Station
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:17.75,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Cool it with the gawking! \NThey'll know we're from Gunma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:21.48,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,But everything's flashing! \NI don't know where to look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.48,0:14:22.25,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:24.93,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Kimari! Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.93,0:14:26.06,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave me behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.06,0:14:28.13,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! That's not her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:29.89,sign_20815_302_Kabukicho_Ichiba,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Kabukicho Ichibangai
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.11,0:14:31.66,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kabukicho...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.66,0:14:33.39,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You've never been here before?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:37.14,sign_20941_304_Ladies__Cabaret_,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies' Cabaret Club
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:37.14,sign_20941_305_Mahjong,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Mahjong
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:37.14,sign_20941_306_3F_Rental_Rooms,sign,0000,0000,0000,,3F\NRental Rooms
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:36.69,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been here at night, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.69,0:14:40.42,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'd be spending the\Nnight at Megu-chan's, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:40.77,sign_21031_309_Free_Information,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Free Information Center
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.09,0:14:43.02,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,You don't think the police'll \Ntake us in, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.47,0:14:47.07,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine, but your school might \Nget mad at you if they find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:48.53,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Just for walking around?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.81,0:14:50.78,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it is Kabukicho...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:53.78,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Just act like you're in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.15,0:14:56.04,Main,host,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, here for a good time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:15:01.74,Main,host,0000,0000,0000,,Just for a bit. Just stop in for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.49,0:15:02.48,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm with friends! I'm with friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.48,0:15:03.92,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.24,0:15:06.30,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,It's funny. Just let it play out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:08.17,sign_21730_321_Free_Information,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Free Information Center\NInformation on Entertainment, Bars
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:08.17,sign_21730_322_This_way_to_entr,sign,0000,0000,0000,,This way to entrance
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:11.54,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,I found it! The Antarctic \Nexpedition informal meet-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:12.93,sign_21817_323_Orange,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Orange
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:12.93,sign_21817_324_Reserved_Today_A,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Reserved Today\NAntarctic Expedition Informal\NMeet-up
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:12.93,sign_21817_325_Sexy_Delicious__,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Sexy Delicious!\NMeat Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.54,0:15:12.60,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:20.44,sign_21889_328_Information_Cent,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Information Center
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:20.44,sign_21889_330_Come_right_in_,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Come right in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.13,0:15:15.57,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, do it just like we planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.57,0:15:19.48,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,But this only says "lure someone out."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:20.44,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.67,0:15:23.51,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there are normally a lot of \Nmale participants in an expedition,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:25.38,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought, being high school girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:28.40,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking about seducing them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:30.56,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Shirase-chan is beautiful, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.56,0:15:32.32,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Me? No, I didn't mean me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:35.40,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, were you planning \Nto make one of us do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:36.83,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.17,0:15:38.35,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,They're here! What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.35,0:15:39.49,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Kimari! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.91,0:15:40.66,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,No! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:40.66,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Kimari! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:42.04,sign_22554_345_Information_Cent,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Information Center
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:42.04,sign_22554_346_Cabaret_Club_Gir,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Cabaret Club Girls' Bar
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:42.04,sign_22554_348_Marilyn,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Marilyn
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:49.37,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,How old-fashioned are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.37,0:15:51.09,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Then you do it, Hinata-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:52.87,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Look! If we don't do something, \Nthey'll go without us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.87,0:15:53.68,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Show some leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:54.58,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I'm wearing pants!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.58,0:15:56.54,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Your breasts, then! Stick out your breasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.54,0:15:57.47,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Are you mocking me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:15:59.27,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, the best breasts belong to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:00.44,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.44,0:16:02.39,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Go! You wanna go to Antarctica, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:05.81,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It's not fair! You are the \None who came up with this plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:08.00,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,No! Besides, it can't be me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:09.39,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't it be you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:10.53,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:18.28,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.05,0:16:21.34,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,She never gives up, does she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.36,0:16:24.92,Main,ketsu,0000,0000,0000,,Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:26.74,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you bow to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.74,0:16:28.55,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,What is this, school? \NAre you an honor student?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:30.61,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I told you it couldn't be me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:31.42,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:33.22,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,They know me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:35.93,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,So if they see me, they'll catch...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:38.89,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh. There's three of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:40.39,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Run.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:44.19,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:48.48,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:53.57,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata-chan, you run fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:55.61,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Over short distances, sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:57.57,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Think we should split up for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:16:59.06,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:01.01,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Where should we meet up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.01,0:17:01.92,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Coordinate with cell phones!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:03.41,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:10.34,sign_24609_383_Secret_Path_of_M,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Secret Path of Memories
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.72,0:17:13.63,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,They're still chasing us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:16.30,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,They're part of the expedition team, \Nso they've got tons of stamina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.47,0:17:19.47,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Should we split up, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:22.21,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.21,0:17:22.97,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.28,0:17:25.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.49,0:17:30.41,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.18,0:17:34.00,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking... this is pretty fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.00,0:17:34.70,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:39.17,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's like... motion!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:44.67,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like my youth is in motion!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:50.96,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... this is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.58,0:17:56.43,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Like anything could happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.39,0:18:00.01,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Like I could make anything happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.96,0:18:07.60,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,The scenery that surrounds me every \Nday is changing at a dizzying rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:14.88,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Drinking outside really is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:16.40,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:18.12,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go drinking over there today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.21,0:18:20.82,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:19:01.66,sign_27289_404_Cafe_Room,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Cafe Room
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:19:01.66,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to exhaust \Nyourselves running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.22,0:19:04.94,Main,sign,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like we were trying to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.55,0:19:06.77,Main,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Though {\i1}she{\i0} actually might.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:07.41,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Kanae.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.65,0:19:09.58,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,But... Shirase-chan said...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:12.78,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she said you'd have \Nour heads if you caught us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.78,0:19:14.17,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I never said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:17.69,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,This is quite a plan you \Ncame up with, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:20.97,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, get a male \Nexpedition member on your side
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:23.02,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,so he'll smuggle you on board, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.02,0:19:24.43,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,You naughty girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:26.31,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Whose idea was this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.26,0:19:30.15,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.15,0:19:31.44,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Shirase-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:36.51,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,I've told you many times before: \Nwe can't take you with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.51,0:19:39.91,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,It may be a civilian expedition, \Nbut there are strict requirements for—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.91,0:19:41.19,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.19,0:19:42.82,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I know I'm being unreasonable!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.33,0:19:46.72,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,But... I really want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:51.11,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Because... my mother is waiting there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.11,0:19:55.52,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.93,0:19:58.84,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.84,0:20:00.14,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,It's just what it looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.83,0:20:02.59,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,You're having trouble with funding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.21,0:20:06.46,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Let me become one of your sponsors!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:09.66,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,If you take me along, \Nyou can have the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.72,0:20:16.61,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,She really thought this through, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.16,0:20:18.43,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.43,0:20:21.69,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Come to Fremantle on December 1st.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.04,0:20:22.97,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.97,0:20:24.37,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you expected to hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.94,0:20:29.75,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry \Nabout us. We're going,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.67,0:20:31.73,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:37.23,Flashback,vo,0000,0000,0000,,Takako! Takako!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:41.61,Flashback,vo,0000,0000,0000,,Takako! Takako!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:46.09,Flashback,vo,0000,0000,0000,,Takako! Takako!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.94,0:20:52.83,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I do understand how she feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:55.22,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's been three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.22,0:21:01.37,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Are we really okay for funding, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.76,0:21:03.67,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,I told you before, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.67,0:21:07.66,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,It might be tough, but I have lots of ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:12.60,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Shiraishi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.36,0:21:15.67,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. And here's step one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:27.93,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:33.46,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't get too down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.46,0:21:35.19,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,It's not necessarily ove—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:37.78,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost there if I'd had a little \Nmore money she would have taken it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.78,0:21:40.27,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,so I just need a little more and \Nshe'll definitely accept it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:42.89,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,A glass-half-full type, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.89,0:21:44.12,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.12,0:21:47.80,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you'd have to be, to get this done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.80,0:21:48.66,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.95,0:21:51.39,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,However!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:53.48,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,I am introducing an emergency motion!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.48,0:21:56.58,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,I request a dismissal of \NKobuchizawa Shirase as group leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:21:57.39,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,All in favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.39,0:21:57.94,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.94,0:21:59.34,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Majority rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.34,0:22:02.54,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, you are hereby dismissed as leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.64,0:22:06.47,Main,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's go to Antarctica!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.88,0:22:08.17,Main,all,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.23,0:22:10.47,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
